[Winter 1941]

00:04:27.370 --> 00:04:28.630
[The fires of World War II]

00:04:28.630 --> 00:04:30.030
[hung heavy over Europe and Asia.]

00:04:30.230 --> 00:04:32.320
[With half of China fallen under the
iron heel of the Japanese invaders,]

00:04:32.350 --> 00:04:35.070
