Hello.

00:06:13.210 --> 00:06:14.210
How can I help you?

00:06:14.630 --> 00:06:16.890
I'm He Xian, manager
of Hong Kong Huilong Bank.

00:06:16.890 --> 00:06:20.690
I'm here to apply for a Macau
financial services operating license.

00:06:21.860 --> 00:06:26.710
[Pier 12: Macau - Hong Kong]

00:06:26.790 --> 00:06:32.540
[Macau All-Sectors Charity Gala
for National Salvation]

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:43.330
[Yu, Tanka]

00:06:43.330 --> 00:06:44.480
Father, Mother,

00:06:44.710 --> 00:06:46.390
they're putting on a play at the pier.

00:06:46.390 --> 00:06:47.860
[Macau All-Sectors Charity Gala
for National Salvation]

00:06:49.570 --> 00:06:51.140
[Yokohama Specie Bank, Macau Branch]

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.000
The rise and fall of a nation

00:06:59.000 --> 00:06:59.120
concerns every one of its citizens.

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:00.570
[Fundraising for National Salvation]

00:07:00.570 --> 00:07:03.610
Compatriots, we urge you
to donate generously.

00:07:04.060 --> 00:07:05.600
Great, I want to donate too.

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:08.980
Here's mine.

00:07:09.980 --> 00:07:10.860
Let's go and donate as well.

00:07:10.860 --> 00:07:11.100
♪ Little sister, oh ♪

00:07:11.100 --> 00:07:11.460
Okay.

00:07:11.980 --> 00:07:12.390
Yu,

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:13.190
my family is donating 30 avos.

00:07:13.190 --> 00:07:13.510
Thank you.

00:07:13.510 --> 00:07:13.830
♪ Go out to sea with the net, hey ♪

00:07:13.830 --> 00:07:14.960
Yu, I donate 10 avos.

