Good.

00:07:15.740 --> 00:07:16.890
Yu, I donate 30 avos.

00:07:17.420 --> 00:07:18.150
Yu, I donate 30 avos.

00:07:18.150 --> 00:07:18.240
♪ Cast and pull, again and again, oh ♪

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:19.370
Yu, I donate 50 avos.

00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:20.610
Yu, I donate 30 avos.

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:21.870
Yu, I donate 50 avos.

00:07:21.870 --> 00:07:22.180
Please tell them—

00:07:22.180 --> 00:07:22.800
♪ My good sister, oh ♪

00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:24.510
they mustn't think our donations
are too small.

00:07:24.510 --> 00:07:24.810
Of course,

00:07:24.810 --> 00:07:25.450
I will.

00:07:28.660 --> 00:07:31.200
♪ Little sister, oh ♪

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:35.710
♪ Let's work as one, oh ♪

00:07:36.860 --> 00:07:43.210
♪ And plan it well together, hey-lo ♪

00:07:44.580 --> 00:07:46.440
♪ Brother, oh ♪

00:07:47.330 --> 00:07:50.240
♪ The haul is plenty, hey ♪

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:51.870
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

00:07:52.610 --> 00:07:53.900
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

00:07:53.900 --> 00:07:55.380
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

00:08:00.860 --> 00:08:01.540
Thank you.

00:08:03.520 --> 00:08:04.440
Mr. Lok Pak.

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:05.950
Mr. Suzuki,

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:07.770
what can I do for you?

00:08:07.770 --> 00:08:08.620
The charity performance just now

00:08:08.620 --> 00:08:09.950
openly violated the ban

00:08:09.950 --> 00:08:11.810
by singing anti-Japanese songs.

00:08:11.830 --> 00:08:13.070
As a government official,

00:08:13.070 --> 00:08:15.070
why haven't you taken legal action?

00:08:15.330 --> 00:08:16.120
Oh,

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:18.310
my apologies—

00:08:18.310 --> 00:08:19.620
I truly didn't notice earlier.

00:08:19.620 --> 00:08:20.600
Thinking back now,

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:21.500
that song

00:08:22.570 --> 00:08:23.830
was indeed anti-Japanese.

00:08:23.830 --> 00:08:24.630
It really was.

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:25.710
But the performance

00:08:25.710 --> 00:08:26.180
has already ended—

00:08:26.180 --> 00:08:26.920
[Lok Pak, Deputy Director
of Macau Economics Bureau]

00:08:26.920 --> 00:08:27.830
it's too late to shut it down now.

00:08:27.830 --> 00:08:28.480
Tell you what,

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:29.560
if anything like this happens again,

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:30.830
I'll be sure to notify the police

00:08:30.830 --> 00:08:31.630
and have it stopped immediately.

00:08:31.630 --> 00:08:33.280
We'll have it stopped right away.

00:08:33.280 --> 00:08:33.659
Hey,

00:08:33.900 --> 00:08:34.500
Miss Qiao,

00:08:34.520 --> 00:08:35.870
I'd like to donate five thousand here.

00:08:35.870 --> 00:08:38.900
[Ichiro Suzuki, Manager
of the Yokohama Specie Bank, Macau Branch]

00:08:59.850 --> 00:09:00.850
Stop right there!

00:09:03.210 --> 00:09:04.270
What are you doing?

00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:05.400
Step back!

00:09:05.450 --> 00:09:06.910
Why are you arresting her?

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:07.760
Mr. Liang,

00:09:08.470 --> 00:09:09.350
this Tanka girl

00:09:09.350 --> 00:09:10.660
came to deliver donations to us,

00:09:10.660 --> 00:09:11.990
and they just arrested her.

00:09:11.990 --> 00:09:13.380
On what grounds are you arresting her?

00:09:13.380 --> 00:09:15.230
I was the one who notified the police

00:09:15.230 --> 00:09:16.690
to legally intercept her.

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:17.940
This girl

00:09:17.940 --> 00:09:19.570
came to deliver patriotic donations
to us.

00:09:19.570 --> 00:09:21.110
What business is that of you Japanese?

00:09:21.110 --> 00:09:22.200
As everyone knows,

00:09:22.310 --> 00:09:23.710
the Tanka are outcastes—

00:09:23.710 --> 00:09:26.070
for thousands of years, they've only
been allowed to live on boats,

00:09:26.070 --> 00:09:28.210
forbidden to set foot
on shore for generations.

00:09:28.210 --> 00:09:29.280
Her feet

00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:31.590
have no right to step
onto the coast of Macau.

00:09:31.590 --> 00:09:32.920
Nonsense!

00:09:33.020 --> 00:09:34.350
[Liang Yanming, Standing Committee Member
of the Kuomintang Macau Branch]

00:09:34.350 --> 00:09:36.490
Since when has Macau had such a law?

00:09:37.300 --> 00:09:37.920
Exactly!

00:09:38.110 --> 00:09:39.880
A Chinese person setting foot
on Chinese land—

00:09:39.880 --> 00:09:41.040
what right do you Japanese have
to interfere?

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:41.490
Yeah!

00:09:41.850 --> 00:09:42.690
This has been

00:09:43.110 --> 00:09:43.940
your own

00:09:43.940 --> 00:09:45.690
Chinese custom for centuries.

00:09:46.470 --> 00:09:47.780
I reported it to the police

00:09:47.780 --> 00:09:48.520
to lawfully prevent

00:09:48.520 --> 00:09:50.050
a Tanka from coming ashore.

00:09:56.350 --> 00:09:58.150
Alright, alright, settle down.

00:09:58.350 --> 00:10:00.080
It's not a big amount after all.

00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:03.180
Miss Qiao,

00:10:03.490 --> 00:10:04.570
look, here's what we can do:

00:10:04.570 --> 00:10:06.070
let's just pretend this young girl
never came.

00:10:06.070 --> 00:10:06.490
[Qiao Yinwan, Young Violinist]

00:10:06.490 --> 00:10:08.070
I'll make up her donation—

00:10:08.190 --> 00:10:10.320
I'll contribute ten times the amount.

00:10:10.450 --> 00:10:10.950
You two,

00:10:10.950 --> 00:10:12.420
take the girl back to her boat right now.

00:10:12.420 --> 00:10:12.920
Wait!

00:10:13.610 --> 00:10:14.460
Dr. Lok Pak,

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:15.900
this isn't about the money.

00:10:15.900 --> 00:10:17.950
This is
about this Chinese girl's dignity,

00:10:17.950 --> 00:10:20.190
and about the patriotism
of all Tanka fishermen.

00:10:20.190 --> 00:10:22.040
Today, I must take this donation,

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:23.640
and no one is taking her away.

00:10:23.730 --> 00:10:24.530
That's right—

00:10:24.830 --> 00:10:26.170
she really can't leave.

00:10:26.300 --> 00:10:26.470
[Gonçalves, Inspector General
of the Macau Police Department]

00:10:26.470 --> 00:10:28.610
Mr. Suzuki,
just what are you trying to do?

00:10:28.610 --> 00:10:30.420
Since the police have confirmed

00:10:30.420 --> 00:10:32.310
that this Tanka individual
came ashore illegally,

00:10:32.310 --> 00:10:35.450
the money in her hands
naturally constitutes illegal funds.

00:10:35.450 --> 00:10:36.350
I demand

00:10:36.350 --> 00:10:39.090
the police immediately confiscate
all donated funds,

00:10:39.090 --> 00:10:40.590
conduct a full investigation,

00:10:40.590 --> 00:10:41.520
and deal with the offender

00:10:41.520 --> 00:10:42.540
according to the law.

00:10:42.540 --> 00:10:43.280
No way!

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:45.350
Our event

00:10:45.350 --> 00:10:47.470
was officially approved
by the Macau government.

00:10:47.470 --> 00:10:48.880
I now believe the Japanese

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:50.310
are making a mountain

00:10:50.310 --> 00:10:51.310
out of a molehill here—

00:10:51.310 --> 00:10:52.690
twisting the situation
and causing trouble.

00:10:52.690 --> 00:10:53.810
Inspector General Gonçalves,

00:10:53.810 --> 00:10:55.180
if in broad daylight

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:57.940
your Portuguese-Macau police refuse
to enforce the law

00:10:57.940 --> 00:11:00.230
and openly indulge
and shield the Chinese,

00:11:00.230 --> 00:11:01.330
then we Japanese

00:11:01.330 --> 00:11:03.020
will also no longer abide

00:11:03.050 --> 00:11:05.850
by any of Macau's laws and regulations
from now on.

00:11:08.690 --> 00:11:09.700
Mr. Liang,

00:11:09.880 --> 00:11:11.540
I apologize for what happened today.

00:11:11.540 --> 00:11:12.920
Since the police have received a report,

00:11:12.920 --> 00:11:14.070
the fundraising must be suspended.

00:11:14.070 --> 00:11:15.810
Please hand over the donations
to the police

00:11:15.810 --> 00:11:17.830
for temporary confiscation;
they will be returned after verification.

00:11:17.830 --> 00:11:19.330
Stop our fundraising?

00:11:19.330 --> 00:11:21.330
By what right
do you stop our fundraising?

00:11:21.330 --> 00:11:21.990
What right?

00:11:22.090 --> 00:11:23.550
This makes no sense at all!

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:26.850
I'm sorry, I never thought
it would come to this.

00:11:26.850 --> 00:11:27.760
It's all my fault.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:28.540
I won't come ashore again,

00:11:28.540 --> 00:11:29.540
never again.

00:11:29.540 --> 00:11:31.970
Please don't confiscate
so many people's donations.

00:11:31.970 --> 00:11:33.440
So now you regret it?

00:11:33.830 --> 00:11:36.470
Who told you Chinese
to lose your own country's territory?

00:11:36.470 --> 00:11:38.680
You think you're worthy
of loving your country

00:11:38.680 --> 00:11:39.610
here in Macau?

00:11:42.070 --> 00:11:42.710
Here, hold this.

00:11:42.710 --> 00:11:43.600
Hey, Xian,

00:11:43.780 --> 00:11:44.690
don't be rash!

00:11:48.300 --> 00:11:49.020
Wait!

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:54.570
Officer,

00:11:54.940 --> 00:11:55.800
I'd like to ask:

00:11:55.830 --> 00:11:57.940
on what basis do you claim
this young lady

00:11:57.940 --> 00:11:59.270
came ashore illegally?

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.140
Wasn't it just explained?

00:12:01.260 --> 00:12:02.730
According to Macau custom.

00:12:02.730 --> 00:12:04.070
Then let me ask this:

00:12:04.070 --> 00:12:04.800
in Macau,

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:05.850
which carries greater weight—

00:12:05.850 --> 00:12:06.850
custom or the law?

00:12:07.110 --> 00:12:08.170
The law, of course.

00:12:08.420 --> 00:12:09.330
But Macau's law

00:12:09.330 --> 00:12:11.160
has no specific provision on this matter.

00:12:11.160 --> 00:12:12.440
But Macau has commercial law.

00:12:12.440 --> 00:12:13.310
And that law states that,

00:12:13.310 --> 00:12:14.560
as an international free port,

00:12:14.560 --> 00:12:16.900
anyone coming to Macau
to engage in international activities—

00:12:16.900 --> 00:12:18.450
regardless of nationality, gender,

00:12:18.450 --> 00:12:19.400
age, or status—

00:12:19.400 --> 00:12:20.930
may enter and leave freely.

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:22.170
Isn't that correct?

00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:24.090
That is indeed true.

00:12:24.090 --> 00:12:26.150
But that applies to businesspeople.

00:12:26.380 --> 00:12:28.310
What does that have to do with this?

00:12:28.470 --> 00:12:29.440
Everything—

00:12:29.880 --> 00:12:30.520
because

00:12:30.770 --> 00:12:32.100
she is my client.

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:35.160
Your client?

00:12:39.300 --> 00:12:41.440
I'm He Xian, manager
of Hong Kong Huilong Bank.

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:42.560
I came to Macau today

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:44.780
to obtain a financial services license.

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:46.910
This is the permit I've just received,

00:12:47.160 --> 00:12:48.020
authorizing me to engage
in financial activities

00:12:48.020 --> 00:12:48.630
in Macau,

00:12:48.800 --> 00:12:50.180
such as stocks, securities,

00:12:50.180 --> 00:12:52.260
and currency exchange,
effective immediately.

00:12:52.260 --> 00:12:53.320
Please take a look.

00:12:55.940 --> 00:12:56.940
It appears valid.

00:12:57.570 --> 00:12:58.280
Good.

00:13:00.610 --> 00:13:01.400
Young lady,

00:13:01.800 --> 00:13:02.800
what's your name?

00:13:03.780 --> 00:13:04.900
My name is Yu.

00:13:05.180 --> 00:13:06.310
Miss Yu,

00:13:06.730 --> 00:13:07.760
my name is He Xian.

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:08.920
I run a bank.

00:13:08.920 --> 00:13:10.520
Don't worry if you don't understand
everything that follows,

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:12.440
but as long as you agree
to entrust this money to me,

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:13.520
the police here

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:14.880
won't dare confiscate these donations.

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:15.450
And you'll

00:13:15.450 --> 00:13:17.450
be able to enter Macau
with your head held high—

00:13:17.450 --> 00:13:18.850
no one can make you leave.

00:13:19.090 --> 00:13:19.900
Understood?

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:22.590
Say you agree!

00:13:22.590 --> 00:13:25.470
Say you agree!

00:13:26.470 --> 00:13:27.400
I agree.

00:13:29.900 --> 00:13:30.560
Officer,

00:13:30.900 --> 00:13:31.560
as you can see,

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:33.740
Miss Yu is now my client—

00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:35.140
a person engaged

00:13:35.140 --> 00:13:37.000
in business activities in Macau.

00:13:37.110 --> 00:13:38.180
Under Macau's law,

00:13:38.330 --> 00:13:40.310
she has the right to enter and leave.

00:13:40.310 --> 00:13:41.440
Please release her.

00:13:41.690 --> 00:13:42.520
Well said!

00:13:42.520 --> 00:13:44.810
Bravo!

00:13:45.640 --> 00:13:46.710
Release her now!

00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:50.810
Hold on.

00:13:53.380 --> 00:13:54.180
You're saying

00:13:54.330 --> 00:13:55.560
she's your client.

00:13:56.140 --> 00:13:56.990
Then tell me,

00:13:57.440 --> 00:14:00.230
what financial service
has she commissioned you to handle?

00:14:00.230 --> 00:14:01.230
I must remind you—

00:14:01.450 --> 00:14:04.180
fabricating a non-existent
business transaction

00:14:04.180 --> 00:14:06.040
is also a violation of Macau's law.

00:14:06.040 --> 00:14:07.420
What financial services

00:14:07.420 --> 00:14:09.020
does your Specie Bank offer?

00:14:09.380 --> 00:14:11.240
We cover all financial services,

00:14:11.380 --> 00:14:12.760
of course.

00:14:13.420 --> 00:14:14.300
Good.

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:21.470
[Agency Collection and Payment]
[Foreign Exchange]

00:14:21.470 --> 00:14:22.380
Then let's go

00:14:22.640 --> 00:14:24.350
with foreign exchange trading.

00:14:24.350 --> 00:14:26.020
I represent this client of mine

00:14:26.020 --> 00:14:27.350
in doing business with your bank—

00:14:27.350 --> 00:14:29.110
placing an order to trade forex.

00:14:29.110 --> 00:14:29.610
That qualifies

00:14:29.610 --> 00:14:32.440
as a legitimate financial transaction,
doesn't it?

00:14:32.440 --> 00:14:34.170
What does she know about forex?

00:14:34.230 --> 00:14:34.560
Besides,

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:36.690
our minimum margin for forex trading

00:14:36.690 --> 00:14:38.350
is a hundred dollars.

00:14:38.590 --> 00:14:40.560
How can she place an order
with that little money?

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:42.810
I can extend a loan to my client.

00:14:46.790 --> 00:14:47.690
Miss Yu,

00:14:48.020 --> 00:14:49.440
how much do you have in total?

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:51.070
It's 28.57 patacas.

00:14:52.310 --> 00:14:52.940
Alright,

00:14:53.730 --> 00:14:55.190
28.57 patacas.

00:14:55.660 --> 00:14:56.570
And here—

00:14:56.570 --> 00:14:58.160
I have 131.6 patacas.

00:14:58.160 --> 00:14:58.920
Now,

00:14:58.920 --> 00:15:00.800
I'm lending you all of this money.

00:15:00.880 --> 00:15:01.490
If it loses,

00:15:01.490 --> 00:15:02.350
the loss is on me.

00:15:02.350 --> 00:15:03.140
If it profits,

00:15:03.140 --> 00:15:04.710
all the proceeds go to you.

00:15:05.070 --> 00:15:05.820
Understood?

00:15:09.380 --> 00:15:10.280
Then

00:15:10.280 --> 00:15:11.080
it's settled.

00:15:16.150 --> 00:15:17.020
Now

00:15:17.020 --> 00:15:18.570
may I place an order

00:15:18.570 --> 00:15:20.350
on behalf of my client with your bank?

00:15:20.350 --> 00:15:21.090
May I ask

00:15:21.090 --> 00:15:22.790
what you intend to buy, sir?

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:32.420
[Moscow][Germany]

00:15:39.640 --> 00:15:40.590
A short position

00:15:40.830 --> 00:15:41.890
on the German Mark.

00:15:42.940 --> 00:15:44.800
You're shorting the German Mark?

00:15:46.830 --> 00:15:47.460
Xian,

00:15:47.830 --> 00:15:49.570
isn't that the other way around?

00:15:49.570 --> 00:15:50.230
No mistake.

00:15:50.440 --> 00:15:52.140
I want to short the German Mark,

00:15:52.140 --> 00:15:53.670
with same-day settlement.

00:15:53.830 --> 00:15:55.040
What's the maximum

00:15:55.040 --> 00:15:56.170
leverage you allow?

00:15:56.190 --> 00:15:57.310
Retail clients get five times.

00:15:57.310 --> 00:15:58.740
Major clients, up to ten.

00:15:59.060 --> 00:15:59.640
But

00:16:00.280 --> 00:16:02.070
today I'll make an exception for you—

00:16:02.070 --> 00:16:04.240
double the major client limit.

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:05.890
Twenty times leverage.

00:16:06.380 --> 00:16:07.100
Do you dare?

00:16:14.690 --> 00:16:15.190
Fine.

00:16:15.660 --> 00:16:16.720
Twenty times it is.

00:16:17.160 --> 00:16:17.640
Xian!

00:16:17.640 --> 00:16:18.440
Wait a moment.

00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:20.620
Wait a moment, sir.

00:16:21.140 --> 00:16:22.560
While I don't understand finance myself,

00:16:22.560 --> 00:16:23.990
someone in my family works in the field,

00:16:23.990 --> 00:16:25.520
so I've heard a thing or two.

00:16:26.180 --> 00:16:28.450
The Germans are currently advancing
on Moscow,

00:16:28.450 --> 00:16:30.690
and the German Mark
has been steadily rising.

00:16:30.690 --> 00:16:31.210
At a time like this,

00:16:31.210 --> 00:16:33.440
shorting the Mark
on behalf of your client

00:16:33.440 --> 00:16:35.070
with such heavy leverage—

00:16:35.440 --> 00:16:37.970
isn't that just handing money
over to others?

00:16:38.070 --> 00:16:39.030
Miss,

00:16:39.140 --> 00:16:40.540
if I'm willing to place this order,

00:16:40.540 --> 00:16:41.540
I absolutely will not

00:16:41.540 --> 00:16:42.920
betray Miss Yu's trust.

00:16:44.990 --> 00:16:45.310
[Yokohama Specie Bank, Macau Branch]

00:16:45.310 --> 00:16:46.040
Everyone,

00:16:46.780 --> 00:16:47.900
today I,

00:16:48.040 --> 00:16:49.090
He Xian, am determined
to take this short position

00:16:49.090 --> 00:16:50.680
against these Japanese.

00:16:51.520 --> 00:16:52.830
Anyone else who trusts me

00:16:52.830 --> 00:16:56.490
is welcome to authorize me
to place orders on their behalf as well.

00:17:09.660 --> 00:17:10.190
Mr. He,

00:17:12.190 --> 00:17:13.720
I don't have much cash on me,

00:17:17.250 --> 00:17:18.119
but count me in.

00:17:19.319 --> 00:17:19.920
Everyone,

00:17:20.270 --> 00:17:21.440
we're all from Macau.

00:17:21.440 --> 00:17:23.530
Even if you don't know this Mr. He,

00:17:23.530 --> 00:17:24.040
you should at least trust me, Ke Lin.

00:17:24.040 --> 00:17:25.900
[Ke Lin, Physician at Kiang Wu Hospital]

00:17:25.900 --> 00:17:28.230
I believe in Mr. He's judgment
and vision.

00:17:28.380 --> 00:17:29.140
I'm in

00:17:29.550 --> 00:17:30.400
on this trade.

00:17:30.710 --> 00:17:31.510
Well said!

00:17:31.940 --> 00:17:34.270
This time we must stand up
to the Japanese.

00:17:34.270 --> 00:17:35.130
Secretary Lin,

00:17:35.290 --> 00:17:36.440
aside from public funds,

00:17:36.440 --> 00:17:37.710
bet everything else

00:17:37.710 --> 00:17:38.340
we have.

00:17:38.660 --> 00:17:39.210
Okay.

00:17:39.210 --> 00:17:40.270
In that case,

00:17:40.270 --> 00:17:41.140
count me in too.

00:17:41.750 --> 00:17:42.860
Count me in.

00:17:42.860 --> 00:17:43.470
And me!

00:17:43.470 --> 00:17:43.990
Me too!

00:17:44.140 --> 00:17:44.750
I'm in!

00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:45.930
Add me!

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:46.650
Count me in!

00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:47.270
Count me in!

00:17:47.270 --> 00:17:48.140
Count me in!

00:17:48.140 --> 00:17:49.090
Count me in!

00:17:49.110 --> 00:17:49.780
Count me in!

00:17:49.810 --> 00:17:51.160
Count me in!

00:17:51.180 --> 00:17:51.980
Count me in!

00:17:52.110 --> 00:17:52.680
Count me in!

00:17:52.680 --> 00:17:53.710
I'm in too! Me too!

00:17:53.770 --> 00:17:59.490
[Pier 12: Macau - Hong Kong]

00:18:02.100 --> 00:18:04.790
The total is 9,755 patacas.

00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:05.400
Manager,

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:07.180
with 20 times leverage—

00:18:07.180 --> 00:18:08.600
isn't the risk too high?

00:18:08.600 --> 00:18:09.320
Risk?

00:18:10.230 --> 00:18:11.140
What risk?

00:18:11.860 --> 00:18:13.600
At a time when our German allies

00:18:13.950 --> 00:18:14.840
are about to capture

00:18:14.840 --> 00:18:16.550
the Soviet capital,

00:18:16.790 --> 00:18:18.440
shorting the Mark

00:18:18.440 --> 00:18:20.550
is practically handing us money.

00:18:20.770 --> 00:18:21.790
Why refuse it?

00:18:23.530 --> 00:18:24.600
Sir,

00:18:24.600 --> 00:18:25.790
as the bank manager,

00:18:26.450 --> 00:18:27.910
it is my duty to remind you:

00:18:28.250 --> 00:18:29.270
for every 1%

00:18:29.490 --> 00:18:31.400
the Mark rises today,

00:18:31.400 --> 00:18:34.320
you will lose 20% of your principal.

00:18:34.320 --> 00:18:35.690
If it rises 5%,

00:18:36.180 --> 00:18:38.640
your position
will be forcibly liquidated.

00:18:38.990 --> 00:18:39.690
Do you understand?

00:18:39.690 --> 00:18:41.100
I run a bank myself.

00:18:41.290 --> 00:18:42.890
You don't need to lecture me.

00:18:44.970 --> 00:18:45.680
Good!

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:50.040
Notify our Hong Kong branch:

00:18:50.340 --> 00:18:51.030
from now on,

00:18:51.030 --> 00:18:54.340
use that public telephone
as the dedicated forex line.

00:18:54.600 --> 00:18:56.200
Report the German Mark price

00:18:56.950 --> 00:18:58.340
every five minutes

00:18:58.340 --> 00:18:59.250
and display it publicly.

00:18:59.250 --> 00:18:59.980
Understood.

00:19:05.190 --> 00:19:06.450
Current price is 6.71.

00:19:07.140 --> 00:19:08.070
[Client He Xian:
Short Position in German Mark]

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:09.140
Let's begin.

00:19:19.050 --> 00:19:19.790
Mr. He,

00:19:20.110 --> 00:19:21.590
over the past half hour,

00:19:22.180 --> 00:19:25.360
the Mark's cumulative rise
has exceeded 1%.

00:19:25.950 --> 00:19:27.360
Your fellow countrymen

00:19:27.640 --> 00:19:30.840
have already lost a quarter
of their money because of you.

00:19:30.860 --> 00:19:33.390
I'm afraid what's left
will soon be wiped out.

00:19:37.270 --> 00:19:38.230
No rush,

00:19:38.620 --> 00:19:39.750
there's still time.

00:19:41.940 --> 00:19:42.790
Mr. He,

00:19:43.290 --> 00:19:45.020
still hoping to turn it around?

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:48.750
Worth a try.

00:19:59.570 --> 00:20:03.830
[German Mark Exchange Rate: 6.8]

00:20:03.900 --> 00:20:05.100
It's 6.42.

00:20:07.210 --> 00:20:08.690
[German Mark Exchange Rate: 6.42]

00:20:08.690 --> 00:20:10.660
It dropped?

00:20:10.660 --> 00:20:13.360
Yes!

00:20:13.840 --> 00:20:15.050
We've almost doubled our money!

00:20:15.050 --> 00:20:16.320
Doubled!

00:20:16.640 --> 00:20:17.210
Manager,

00:20:17.990 --> 00:20:19.100
what do we do?

00:20:19.490 --> 00:20:21.490
The Mark has been rising for months.

00:20:21.660 --> 00:20:24.250
Investors were bound
to take short-term profits—

00:20:24.250 --> 00:20:26.310
this is just a technical correction.

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:28.030
It'll bounce back soon.

00:20:28.530 --> 00:20:29.660
It has to.

00:20:31.180 --> 00:20:31.990
Is that so?

00:20:32.620 --> 00:20:33.480
Then let's wait

00:20:33.820 --> 00:20:35.250
another five minutes.

00:20:51.420 --> 00:20:52.950
Please announce the price.

00:20:58.920 --> 00:20:59.990
Impossible!

00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:02.630
How can this be?

00:21:09.010 --> 00:21:11.740
Please report the latest price
of the Mark again.

00:21:18.030 --> 00:21:19.110
[German Mark Exchange Rate: 6.42]

00:21:27.530 --> 00:21:30.990
Great!

00:21:30.990 --> 00:21:33.080
A nearly 20% drop in five minutes—

00:21:33.080 --> 00:21:34.280
the Mark has crashed!

00:21:34.770 --> 00:21:35.600
Xian,

00:21:35.600 --> 00:21:37.660
how did you know the Mark would crash?

00:21:38.970 --> 00:21:41.580
You must also be wondering why, right?

00:21:42.250 --> 00:21:44.450
The forex market changes in an instant.

00:21:44.690 --> 00:21:46.840
How could a small
Hong Kong bank owner

00:21:46.840 --> 00:21:47.970
like you predict it?

00:21:48.400 --> 00:21:49.470
You just got lucky.

00:21:50.050 --> 00:21:51.580
That's all it was.

00:21:52.730 --> 00:21:54.860
The forex market does change rapidly,

00:21:55.360 --> 00:21:56.320
but right now,

00:21:56.320 --> 00:21:58.190
there's only one key factor

00:21:58.190 --> 00:21:59.340
determining the exchange rate
of the German Mark—

00:21:59.340 --> 00:22:01.470
the situation in the Battle of Moscow.

00:22:01.770 --> 00:22:03.180
The German army has just suffered

00:22:03.180 --> 00:22:04.780
a devastating defeat there.

00:22:05.470 --> 00:22:06.450
Impossible!

00:22:06.950 --> 00:22:08.270
Since the start of the Soviet-German war,

00:22:08.270 --> 00:22:10.360
the Germans have been advancing nonstop.

00:22:10.360 --> 00:22:12.950
In less than 6 months, they've eliminated
nearly a million Soviet troops.

00:22:12.950 --> 00:22:13.340
And

00:22:13.710 --> 00:22:14.640
they've had Moscow surrounded

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:15.710
for over a month.

00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:18.250
How could the German army
possibly be defeated?

00:22:18.250 --> 00:22:19.290
That question,

00:22:19.750 --> 00:22:20.840
we can ask

00:22:20.840 --> 00:22:22.970
Mr. Ke, who was the first to support me.

00:22:28.730 --> 00:22:29.860
[Moscow][Germany]

00:22:29.860 --> 00:22:31.580
Because in the last three days,

00:22:31.580 --> 00:22:33.490
Germany—which always loves to boast
about its victories—

00:22:33.490 --> 00:22:34.580
hasn't mentioned the Eastern Front

00:22:34.580 --> 00:22:37.550
in its news reports at all.

00:22:37.550 --> 00:22:38.100
Meanwhile,

00:22:38.100 --> 00:22:40.140
the Soviet TASS agency announced

00:22:40.490 --> 00:22:41.550
it would release important news

00:22:41.550 --> 00:22:43.340
about the war situation today.

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:44.400
So?

00:22:44.400 --> 00:22:45.190
So,

00:22:45.490 --> 00:22:47.250
at least three days ago,

00:22:47.600 --> 00:22:48.340
the Red Army had already

00:22:48.340 --> 00:22:50.530
launched a counteroffensive
in the Battle of Moscow

00:22:50.530 --> 00:22:53.640
and achieved a major victory
within those three days.

00:22:55.100 --> 00:22:57.510
The German offensive has been broken,

00:22:58.160 --> 00:22:59.920
and they are headed for defeat.

00:23:01.140 --> 00:23:01.880
Right now,

00:23:01.880 --> 00:23:03.880
it's 10:30 a.m. in Moscow.

00:23:04.290 --> 00:23:05.230
TASS's announcement has been

00:23:05.230 --> 00:23:06.750
out for half an hour.

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:08.440
News agencies worldwide

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:10.510
must be scrambling to relay the news

00:23:10.510 --> 00:23:12.340
of Moscow's victory.

00:23:13.100 --> 00:23:13.820
That's why

00:23:14.100 --> 00:23:16.420
the German Mark suddenly crashed—

00:23:16.420 --> 00:23:18.440
and this is only the beginning.

00:23:34.840 --> 00:23:37.530
The Mark has fallen 30%.

00:23:37.710 --> 00:23:40.380
We've received an urgent telegram
from our Yokohama HQ:

00:23:40.380 --> 00:23:44.050
close all short positions
on the Mark immediately.

00:23:50.680 --> 00:23:51.540
I admit defeat!

00:23:51.900 --> 00:23:52.830
I'll settle now!

00:23:53.470 --> 00:23:54.870
Let's settle right away.

00:23:56.230 --> 00:23:57.960
Now you're in a hurry to settle?

00:23:58.580 --> 00:24:00.030
The market hasn't closed yet—

00:24:00.030 --> 00:24:00.830
I'm in no rush.

00:24:02.010 --> 00:24:03.080
It's only down

00:24:03.080 --> 00:24:04.210
a little over 20%.

00:24:05.180 --> 00:24:05.920
I'll settle

00:24:05.920 --> 00:24:07.180
at 30%.

00:24:09.740 --> 00:24:11.070
[Ticket Check]

00:24:11.130 --> 00:24:13.170
[Macau - Hong Kong]

00:24:15.750 --> 00:24:16.620
Mr. He,

00:24:17.210 --> 00:24:19.430
your ship to Hong Kong departs soon.

00:24:19.970 --> 00:24:21.460
Why miss it?

00:24:21.880 --> 00:24:24.010
Unless you're not planning to return?

00:24:24.250 --> 00:24:25.180
That's alright.

00:24:25.440 --> 00:24:27.040
A ticket's only 8.5 patacas.

00:24:27.270 --> 00:24:28.180
If I miss this one,

00:24:28.180 --> 00:24:29.580
I'll just catch the next.

00:24:29.940 --> 00:24:33.750
Nobody leave!

00:24:34.180 --> 00:24:34.770
Let's see how much he has to pay.

00:24:34.770 --> 00:24:36.230
Let's settle it at 30%.

00:24:37.100 --> 00:24:37.440
No.

00:24:38.860 --> 00:24:39.520
I'll settle

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:41.750
at 40%.

00:24:41.750 --> 00:24:43.030
Is that acceptable?

00:24:43.030 --> 00:24:44.690
Trying to cut your losses now?

00:24:45.600 --> 00:24:46.180
Alright.

00:24:46.730 --> 00:24:48.690
Don't say I didn't give you a chance.

00:24:48.690 --> 00:24:49.970
Settle at 45%.

00:24:50.080 --> 00:24:51.180
With your principal,

00:24:51.180 --> 00:24:52.380
that makes it exactly ten-to-one.

00:24:52.380 --> 00:24:53.230
Rounding down,

00:24:53.230 --> 00:24:54.120
you owe

00:24:54.120 --> 00:24:55.050
97,000 patacas.

00:24:56.840 --> 00:24:57.340
This...

00:24:57.940 --> 00:24:59.030
I'm not finished.

00:24:59.940 --> 00:25:01.510
If you want to settle quickly,

00:25:01.510 --> 00:25:03.110
then you—starting with you—

00:25:03.230 --> 00:25:04.770
must lead all Japanese present here

00:25:04.770 --> 00:25:06.440
in bowing and apologizing
to this young lady, Yu,

00:25:06.440 --> 00:25:07.750
for your insulting remarks

00:25:07.750 --> 00:25:08.950
against the Chinese.

00:25:09.010 --> 00:25:10.600
And you will
stop your promotional activities,

00:25:10.600 --> 00:25:11.660
pack up, and leave.

00:25:12.530 --> 00:25:13.190
Otherwise,

00:25:14.250 --> 00:25:15.910
none of us will board the ship.

00:25:16.140 --> 00:25:18.140
We'll stay and keep you company
until the end.

00:25:18.140 --> 00:25:18.970
Yes!

00:25:18.970 --> 00:25:24.050
Until the end!

00:25:26.920 --> 00:25:28.100
If this drags on

00:25:28.100 --> 00:25:29.630
and we really miss our ship,

00:25:29.880 --> 00:25:31.810
I'll have to raise the price again.

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:39.650
We're sorry.

00:25:40.140 --> 00:25:40.940
We were wrong.

00:25:41.470 --> 00:25:43.070
Please forgive our offense.

00:25:43.950 --> 00:25:45.900
Good!

00:25:56.690 --> 00:25:57.620
That felt right!

00:26:06.510 --> 00:26:07.380
Miss Yu,

00:26:07.750 --> 00:26:09.380
this is your principal plus profit.

00:26:09.380 --> 00:26:11.400
I'll waive the commission on this trade,

00:26:11.400 --> 00:26:13.290
and you can keep the money I lent you.

00:26:13.290 --> 00:26:15.220
That makes 1,600 patacas in total.

00:26:17.320 --> 00:26:18.380
This much?

00:26:18.550 --> 00:26:19.820
Didn't I say?

00:26:19.820 --> 00:26:20.940
"If we lose, the loss is mine.

00:26:20.940 --> 00:26:23.140
If we profit, all the money goes to you. "

00:26:36.140 --> 00:26:37.000
Is all the money

00:26:37.120 --> 00:26:38.720
Is all this for the donation?

00:26:40.790 --> 00:26:41.600
Tang.

00:26:50.600 --> 00:26:51.420
Bravo!

00:26:57.190 --> 00:26:57.840
Yu,

00:26:58.160 --> 00:26:59.600
this commemorative medal

00:26:59.600 --> 00:27:00.490
belongs to you—

00:27:00.660 --> 00:27:02.880
and to all the Tanka people.

00:27:03.230 --> 00:27:04.290
Thank you

00:27:04.290 --> 00:27:05.200
for your contribution
to the resistance effort back home.

00:27:05.200 --> 00:27:06.310
[Macau All-Sectors National Salvation
Charity Gala Commemorative Badge]

00:27:10.290 --> 00:27:11.100
Everyone,

00:27:11.600 --> 00:27:12.730
I have a suggestion.

00:27:12.860 --> 00:27:14.920
The money we won from the Japanese today—

00:27:14.920 --> 00:27:16.680
let's follow Yu's example

00:27:17.010 --> 00:27:18.180
and donate all of it

00:27:18.180 --> 00:27:19.470
to the national salvation fund.

00:27:19.470 --> 00:27:20.550
What do you say?

00:27:20.550 --> 00:27:22.050
Yes, let's do it!

00:27:22.860 --> 00:27:24.510
Good! That's wonderful!

00:27:24.510 --> 00:27:26.630
With these donations,

00:27:26.990 --> 00:27:27.900
it's enough—more than enough now.

00:27:27.900 --> 00:27:29.490
This isn't just about the money anymore.

00:27:29.490 --> 00:27:31.880
It's about standing up for us Chinese.

00:27:31.880 --> 00:27:32.660
Exactly!

00:27:32.660 --> 00:27:34.390
We have Mr. He to thank for this.

00:27:34.950 --> 00:27:36.470
Hey, where is Mr. He?

00:27:36.470 --> 00:27:37.730
Don't bother looking.

00:27:37.900 --> 00:27:40.100
He's already boarded the ship and left.

00:27:44.770 --> 00:27:45.500
Satisfying!

00:27:45.770 --> 00:27:47.010
Absolutely satisfying!

00:27:47.010 --> 00:27:48.440
What a triumphant battle.

00:27:48.440 --> 00:27:50.210
Xian, I'm in awe of you.

00:27:50.840 --> 00:27:52.450
You're still too kind-hearted.

00:27:52.450 --> 00:27:53.940
If you hadn't let them off the hook,

00:27:53.940 --> 00:27:56.070
those Japanese would've been ruined.

00:27:56.270 --> 00:27:58.000
Who said I let them off the hook?

00:27:58.270 --> 00:27:59.200
What do you mean?

00:27:59.340 --> 00:28:00.690
The Mark crashed so fast

00:28:00.690 --> 00:28:02.640
because of a sudden news shock—

00:28:03.010 --> 00:28:04.940
panic in the market is inevitable.

00:28:05.120 --> 00:28:06.600
But the Soviet-German front is vast;

00:28:06.600 --> 00:28:08.490
Moscow is just one point.

00:28:08.990 --> 00:28:10.640
Even if the Germans are defeated there,

00:28:10.640 --> 00:28:13.290
it wouldn't overturn
the entire war situation.

00:28:13.290 --> 00:28:14.820
Once the market calms down,

00:28:14.820 --> 00:28:16.220
there's bound to be a partial recovery.

00:28:16.220 --> 00:28:17.770
You can check later
if you don't believe me—

00:28:17.770 --> 00:28:18.830
by the close today,

00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:22.050
the Mark likely won't have fallen
more than twenty percent.

00:28:22.050 --> 00:28:23.990
So you took advantage of their panic

00:28:23.990 --> 00:28:25.490
and fleeced them again?

00:28:25.950 --> 00:28:27.880
Who else should we fleece
if not the Japanese?

00:28:27.880 --> 00:28:28.940
They had it coming!

00:28:29.400 --> 00:28:30.380
Well done!

00:28:46.050 --> 00:28:48.640
[Huilong Bank, Hong Kong]

00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:49.900
Withdraw everything.

00:28:50.180 --> 00:28:52.140
Sir, are you certain about this?

00:28:52.140 --> 00:28:52.940
Make it quick!

00:28:55.860 --> 00:28:56.730
Well, sir,

00:28:57.320 --> 00:28:59.120
this anonymous account of yours

00:28:59.120 --> 00:28:59.990
holds the largest

00:28:59.990 --> 00:29:02.320
investment amount among all our clients.

00:29:02.660 --> 00:29:03.680
Also,

00:29:03.680 --> 00:29:05.690
you deposited the funds very recently

00:29:05.690 --> 00:29:06.710
and explicitly entrusted us

00:29:06.710 --> 00:29:09.370
with investing in stocks
and foreign exchange.

00:29:09.990 --> 00:29:10.770
However,

00:29:11.840 --> 00:29:13.370
to withdraw such a large sum

00:29:14.420 --> 00:29:16.450
in full,

00:29:16.450 --> 00:29:17.660
our regulations require

00:29:17.660 --> 00:29:18.940
an appointment

00:29:18.940 --> 00:29:19.970
at least one week in advance.

00:29:19.970 --> 00:29:20.660
No.

00:29:21.400 --> 00:29:22.710
I need the money urgently today.

00:29:22.710 --> 00:29:23.770
Where's your boss?

00:29:23.970 --> 00:29:24.880
I'm sorry, sir,

00:29:25.340 --> 00:29:27.160
our manager, Mr. He,
is away in Macau on business.

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:27.530
But even if he were here,

00:29:27.530 --> 00:29:28.840
[Huang Gongjie, Second Helmsman
of the Tai Ho Brotherhood]

00:29:28.840 --> 00:29:30.080
both the stock and forex markets

00:29:30.080 --> 00:29:32.120
are closed for the day now.

00:29:32.270 --> 00:29:33.710
If you want to liquidate your holdings,

00:29:33.710 --> 00:29:35.160
the earliest would be tomorrow.

00:29:35.160 --> 00:29:36.620
I don't care if your manager
is here or not.

00:29:36.620 --> 00:29:37.400
One thing's clear—

00:29:37.400 --> 00:29:38.080
I want my money,

00:29:38.080 --> 00:29:39.150
and I want it now.

00:29:40.450 --> 00:29:41.510
Please don't rush.

00:29:41.710 --> 00:29:43.450
It's not that I won't handle it for you—

00:29:43.450 --> 00:29:45.100
it's simply that the markets are closed.

00:29:45.100 --> 00:29:47.010
Even if I gathered all the cash
we have in the entire bank,

00:29:47.010 --> 00:29:48.540
it still wouldn't be enough

00:29:48.950 --> 00:29:49.820
to cover

00:29:49.820 --> 00:29:50.990
such a large amount.

00:29:52.140 --> 00:29:53.550
I'm withdrawing my—

00:29:57.770 --> 00:29:58.660
Hey, sir,

00:29:58.660 --> 00:29:59.090
please keep your deposit receipt safe.

00:29:59.090 --> 00:29:59.660
[Foreign Exchange & Remittance]

00:29:59.660 --> 00:30:00.880
F-For your anonymous account,

00:30:00.880 --> 00:30:04.140
you'll need this deposit receipt
to make any withdrawals.

00:30:13.950 --> 00:30:15.190
[Liang Zhong, Master of the Hai Yun Hall,
Tai Ho Brotherhood]

00:30:15.190 --> 00:30:15.950
Jie,

00:30:16.900 --> 00:30:18.820
you're not easy to track down.

00:30:19.730 --> 00:30:20.360
Mr. Liang.

00:30:20.360 --> 00:30:21.690
Third Master's orders.

00:30:21.790 --> 00:30:24.530
The brothers are here to take you
back to the society.

00:30:24.530 --> 00:30:25.190
Don't move!

00:30:25.550 --> 00:30:26.340
We're on the same side!

00:30:26.340 --> 00:30:27.620
We're all family here!

00:30:27.620 --> 00:30:28.480
Huang Gongjie,

00:30:28.990 --> 00:30:30.140
when you secretly

00:30:30.140 --> 00:30:32.620
helped the Japanese smuggle tungsten
behind the society's back,

00:30:32.620 --> 00:30:35.080
did you treat
these brothers as family then?

00:30:35.120 --> 00:30:36.190
I'm telling you,

00:30:37.080 --> 00:30:39.480
If you dare to do it,
have the guts to face it.

00:30:40.160 --> 00:30:40.970
Take him back!

00:30:56.440 --> 00:30:58.210
I'm home, kiddos.

00:31:00.010 --> 00:31:01.180
Daddy!

00:31:01.180 --> 00:31:02.510
Here, these are for you.

00:31:03.400 --> 00:31:05.010
Wow, dessert!

00:31:05.790 --> 00:31:06.620
How about that?

00:31:06.620 --> 00:31:07.880
A promise is a promise—

00:31:07.970 --> 00:31:09.100
did Dad keep his word?

00:31:09.100 --> 00:31:10.680
Thanks, Dad!

00:31:10.790 --> 00:31:12.290
Look at you, still so proud of yourself.

00:31:12.290 --> 00:31:13.290
How many times have I said it?

00:31:13.290 --> 00:31:14.550
The kids are teething right now.

00:31:14.550 --> 00:31:16.710
They can't always eat so much sweet stuff.

00:31:16.710 --> 00:31:17.290
Alright,

00:31:17.530 --> 00:31:18.640
my bad.

00:31:18.900 --> 00:31:20.430
I won't buy it anymore then.

00:31:20.750 --> 00:31:21.750
You always say you won't,

00:31:21.750 --> 00:31:23.280
but you keep spoiling them.

00:31:24.580 --> 00:31:25.400
Come, son,

00:31:25.620 --> 00:31:27.180
come with me to see Grandpa first.

00:31:27.180 --> 00:31:27.710
Okay.

00:31:30.180 --> 00:31:30.910
Look at that.

00:31:33.640 --> 00:31:34.050
Renyu.

00:31:34.050 --> 00:31:34.600
Hmm?

00:31:35.140 --> 00:31:36.940
I finally saw it today—

00:31:37.680 --> 00:31:40.640
turns out your Harvard Ph.D. in finance

00:31:40.790 --> 00:31:42.550
doesn't even rank here in Hong Kong.

00:31:42.550 --> 00:31:43.180
[Qiao Renyu, Chief Accountant of HSBC]

00:31:43.180 --> 00:31:43.860
Hmm?

00:31:45.880 --> 00:31:47.440
You don't know finance.

00:31:47.600 --> 00:31:49.800
How can you even judge someone's level?

00:31:50.750 --> 00:31:52.320
There are so many scammers
in this industry—

00:31:52.320 --> 00:31:54.160
you sure you weren't tricked by someone?

00:31:54.160 --> 00:31:55.360
Don't brush it off.

00:31:55.550 --> 00:31:56.710
The guy I met

00:31:56.880 --> 00:31:59.470
took a few thousand dollars scraped
together on the spot to trade forex,

00:31:59.470 --> 00:32:00.990
and in just half an hour,

00:32:00.990 --> 00:32:03.850
made the Japanese side lose
nearly a hundred grand.

00:32:04.620 --> 00:32:06.750
Something like that really happened?

00:32:14.490 --> 00:32:15.250
Grandpa.

00:32:15.380 --> 00:32:16.100
Father,

00:32:16.470 --> 00:32:17.290
I'm back.

00:32:17.660 --> 00:32:18.860
Let us offer incense.

00:32:37.290 --> 00:32:38.890
Descendant of the He family,

00:32:39.100 --> 00:32:40.100
He Xian, present.

00:32:40.940 --> 00:32:41.510
Here.

00:32:41.840 --> 00:32:43.600
Speak truthfully

00:32:43.970 --> 00:32:45.230
before our forebears.

00:32:45.860 --> 00:32:47.190
In your dealings today,

00:32:47.550 --> 00:32:49.690
was there any dishonesty in business?

00:32:51.750 --> 00:32:52.900
None whatsoever.

00:32:53.250 --> 00:32:55.420
Did you break any promises?

00:32:56.180 --> 00:32:57.380
I kept every promise.

00:32:57.550 --> 00:32:59.450
In all other matters,

00:32:59.450 --> 00:33:02.620
have you acted in a way
worthy of our ancestors' teachings

00:33:02.620 --> 00:33:04.140
and your own conscience?

00:33:04.420 --> 00:33:05.600
I, He Xian, have acted

00:33:05.600 --> 00:33:06.750
within my duties

00:33:07.180 --> 00:33:08.780
and with a clear conscience.

00:33:36.920 --> 00:33:38.520
Is everything you said true?

00:33:38.860 --> 00:33:41.790
If I were making it up,
I couldn't spin a tale this legendary.

00:33:41.790 --> 00:33:42.900
Fair enough.

00:33:44.840 --> 00:33:47.620
With the sudden shift
in the Soviet-German war situation,

00:33:47.620 --> 00:33:48.840
hardly any financial experts—

00:33:48.840 --> 00:33:50.940
not just in Hong Kong but worldwide—

00:33:51.140 --> 00:33:52.680
could've predicted it.

00:33:52.680 --> 00:33:53.080
Hmm.

00:33:53.340 --> 00:33:56.210
This Mr. He predicted it that accurately,

00:33:56.680 --> 00:33:58.470
right down to the timing?

00:33:58.470 --> 00:33:59.420
Exactly..

00:33:59.420 --> 00:34:01.330
And to be so bold right

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:02.680
in front of the Japanese—

00:34:02.680 --> 00:34:03.710
daring and sharp.

00:34:05.600 --> 00:34:07.440
But how come

00:34:08.000 --> 00:34:10.719
I've never heard
of such a remarkable colleague?

00:34:10.719 --> 00:34:12.090
On the boat back to Hong Kong,

00:34:12.090 --> 00:34:13.610
someone who knew him mentioned

00:34:13.610 --> 00:34:14.949
his Huilong Bank

00:34:14.949 --> 00:34:17.219
has only been open for three years
in Hong Kong.

00:34:17.219 --> 00:34:20.350
Of course, it's nothing compared
to HSBC's reputation.

00:34:21.550 --> 00:34:22.590
In that case,

00:34:22.590 --> 00:34:23.850
it really goes to show—

00:34:23.940 --> 00:34:25.570
heroes can emerge from anywhere,

00:34:25.570 --> 00:34:26.830
and greatness isn't measured by pedigree.

00:34:26.830 --> 00:34:27.620
Exactly.

00:34:28.030 --> 00:34:29.300
A talent like that—

00:34:29.630 --> 00:34:31.230
I'd love to meet him someday.

00:34:31.989 --> 00:34:32.670
Sure.

00:34:33.320 --> 00:34:34.530
We're all in Hong Kong,

00:34:34.530 --> 00:34:37.719
and he's so passionate about benefit shows
for the Resistance.

00:34:37.719 --> 00:34:38.949
Next time there's an event
for the Resistance,

00:34:38.949 --> 00:34:39.570
I'll invite him.

00:34:39.570 --> 00:34:40.900
I'm sure he'll come.

00:34:42.590 --> 00:34:43.400
Yinwan,

00:34:43.969 --> 00:34:45.949
speaking of these Resistance events—

00:34:45.949 --> 00:34:47.940
could we maybe reduce…

00:34:47.940 --> 00:34:49.630
Could we maybe reduce
how much I appear in public,

00:34:49.630 --> 00:34:50.550
right?

00:34:50.820 --> 00:34:51.940
Every time I join an event like that,
you try to stop me—

00:34:51.940 --> 00:34:53.010
over and over—

00:34:53.010 --> 00:34:54.300
and you never succeed.

00:34:54.900 --> 00:34:55.960
Isn't that tiring?

00:34:56.070 --> 00:34:58.400
I'm genuinely worried about your safety.

00:34:58.840 --> 00:35:01.070
You know what the Japanese
are capable of.

00:35:01.070 --> 00:35:02.590
Don't think just
because Hong Kong and Macau

00:35:02.590 --> 00:35:04.150
are under foreign control now,

00:35:04.150 --> 00:35:05.950
they won't dare act recklessly.

00:35:06.010 --> 00:35:07.340
In just the past few years,

00:35:07.340 --> 00:35:09.320
how many resistance figures
have vanished—

00:35:09.320 --> 00:35:11.710
kidnapped, assassinated, bombed?

00:35:11.760 --> 00:35:12.760
You're fine as you are—

00:35:12.760 --> 00:35:14.440
why provoke them?

00:35:14.800 --> 00:35:15.740
Provoke them?

00:35:17.320 --> 00:35:18.950
Half our country is already

00:35:18.950 --> 00:35:20.280
occupied by the Japanese!

00:35:20.280 --> 00:35:21.400
As a Chinese person,

00:35:21.400 --> 00:35:22.700
promoting resistance
and national salvation—

00:35:22.700 --> 00:35:24.070
and you call that provoking them?

00:35:24.070 --> 00:35:24.940
Alright,

00:35:24.940 --> 00:35:26.110
I misspoke.

00:35:26.940 --> 00:35:28.470
Of course I know we must resist,

00:35:28.470 --> 00:35:29.650
we must save the country—

00:35:29.650 --> 00:35:32.260
haven't I donated every single time?

00:35:32.590 --> 00:35:34.530
But soldiers fight on the front lines,

00:35:34.530 --> 00:35:36.050
officials handle governance in the rear—

00:35:36.050 --> 00:35:37.290
what difference can you,

00:35:37.290 --> 00:35:38.350
a violinist, make?

00:35:38.900 --> 00:35:39.800
And besides,

00:35:39.990 --> 00:35:41.190
these past two years,

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:43.170
doing benefit tours near home

00:35:43.170 --> 00:35:44.170
was one thing,

00:35:44.170 --> 00:35:46.030
but you've gone to Southeast Asia,

00:35:46.030 --> 00:35:47.550
the U.S.—

00:35:47.550 --> 00:35:49.470
running all over the world.

00:35:49.470 --> 00:35:50.450
What are you trying to do?

00:35:50.450 --> 00:35:52.420
I'm rallying overseas Chinese

00:35:52.420 --> 00:35:54.260
to donate for national salvation.

00:35:54.260 --> 00:35:55.200
One thing's clear—

00:35:55.200 --> 00:35:57.230
no more of these tours from now on.

00:35:57.650 --> 00:36:00.250
At most, I'll just donate
more money next time.

00:36:00.380 --> 00:36:01.990
If everyone thought like you,

00:36:01.990 --> 00:36:04.320
our country would have perished already.

00:36:04.320 --> 00:36:06.570
No courage yourself,
and now you won't let me go?

00:36:06.570 --> 00:36:07.280
Next time—

00:36:07.280 --> 00:36:09.150
a hundred times from now—I'll still go!

00:36:09.150 --> 00:36:09.930
You—

00:36:10.130 --> 00:36:11.260
What are you doing?

00:36:11.260 --> 00:36:11.990
Sorry, sorry,

00:36:11.990 --> 00:36:12.740
I didn't mean to.

00:36:12.740 --> 00:36:13.200
Yinwan.

00:36:14.840 --> 00:36:15.470
Yinwan.

00:36:16.550 --> 00:36:17.260
Yinwan.

00:36:22.930 --> 00:36:24.970
[Grand Hall of the Tai Ho Brotherhood]

00:36:24.970 --> 00:36:26.440
Huang Gongjie,

00:36:26.440 --> 00:36:27.590
master of the Hai Bo Hall,

00:36:27.590 --> 00:36:27.760
along with his followers,

00:36:27.760 --> 00:36:29.440
[Huang Sanhe, Supreme Leader
of the Tai Ho Brotherhood]

00:36:29.440 --> 00:36:30.950
has violated the society's code

00:36:30.950 --> 00:36:32.530
by selling out our country to the enemy,

00:36:32.530 --> 00:36:33.930
tarnishing the loyal name
of our Tai Ho Brotherhood

00:36:33.930 --> 00:36:35.580
[Huang Zixia, Master of the Hai Feng Hall,
Tai Ho Brotherhood]

00:36:36.110 --> 00:36:36.940
Brothers!

00:36:37.490 --> 00:36:38.200
Business is booming,

00:36:38.200 --> 00:36:39.380
Greedy Gambler Rong.

00:36:39.380 --> 00:36:40.470
You're doing well.

00:36:40.920 --> 00:36:42.820
Getting rich is up to Mr. Huang.

00:36:42.820 --> 00:36:44.670
We're just the errand boys.

00:36:45.900 --> 00:36:46.440
No need.

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:47.530
Alright, officer.

00:36:50.200 --> 00:36:51.200
Brothers,

00:36:51.320 --> 00:36:52.450
what should be done?

00:36:52.570 --> 00:36:54.990
Kill! Kill! Kill!

00:36:56.450 --> 00:36:58.450
Bring forth the society's justice!

00:37:03.800 --> 00:37:05.860
Huang Gongjie, as hall master,

00:37:06.070 --> 00:37:07.630
led the way in turning traitor.

00:37:07.630 --> 00:37:09.200
The punishment is three stabs, six wounds.

00:37:09.200 --> 00:37:11.570
The rest will each lose an arm

00:37:11.900 --> 00:37:14.360
and be expelled
from the Tai Ho Brotherhood.

00:37:14.380 --> 00:37:16.280
L-Leader, have mercy!

00:37:16.360 --> 00:37:17.170
Leader.

00:37:25.240 --> 00:37:25.970
Fifth Master!

00:37:25.970 --> 00:37:26.450
Fifth Master,

00:37:26.450 --> 00:37:27.630
save me! Fifth Master!

00:37:27.630 --> 00:37:28.740
Don't forget—

00:37:29.030 --> 00:37:31.200
my grandfather and father

00:37:31.200 --> 00:37:32.690
both died for the Tai Ho Brotherhood!

00:37:32.690 --> 00:37:34.900
You swore at their graves

00:37:35.300 --> 00:37:38.200
that I'd be like your own son!

00:37:38.200 --> 00:37:39.200
You have to save me,

00:37:39.200 --> 00:37:40.780
Fifth Master—say something!

00:37:40.780 --> 00:37:41.630
Fifth Master!

00:37:44.380 --> 00:37:45.200
Leader.

00:37:46.360 --> 00:37:47.160
Fifth Master,

00:37:48.280 --> 00:37:50.320
this is about the society's code
and righteousness!

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:52.990
I know. I understand.

00:37:53.220 --> 00:37:54.920
But several lives from Jie's family,
three generations,

00:37:54.920 --> 00:37:57.320
were lost for the Tai Ho Brotherhood.

00:37:57.610 --> 00:37:59.110
Give him a chance to live.

00:37:59.860 --> 00:38:01.050
Death can be spared,

00:38:01.050 --> 00:38:02.280
but punishment cannot.

00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:03.470
Just cut off both his arms,

00:38:03.470 --> 00:38:05.610
then expel him
from the Tai Ho Brotherhood.

00:38:05.610 --> 00:38:06.410
Fifth Master!

00:38:06.450 --> 00:38:07.820
Shut your mouth!

00:38:07.820 --> 00:38:10.110
I'm giving you a chance to live!

00:38:14.420 --> 00:38:15.470
I'm begging you this once.

00:38:15.470 --> 00:38:16.130
Fifth Master,

00:38:16.130 --> 00:38:17.200
no, please don't do this!

00:38:17.200 --> 00:38:17.650
Fifth Master,

00:38:17.650 --> 00:38:18.780
please get up first.

00:38:20.950 --> 00:38:21.950
Huang Gongjie,

00:38:22.260 --> 00:38:24.120
as the leader in turning traitor,

00:38:24.130 --> 00:38:25.920
should have faced
three blades, six wounds.

00:38:25.920 --> 00:38:27.630
Out of respect for the late gang leader,

00:38:27.630 --> 00:38:29.510
let it be handled as he said.

00:38:29.780 --> 00:38:30.670
Untie him.

00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:46.900
Fifth Master,

00:38:47.150 --> 00:38:49.170
you raised me.

00:38:49.170 --> 00:38:51.780
Grant me, Huang Gongjie,
this small dignity—

00:38:51.990 --> 00:38:53.990
do it yourself,

00:38:53.990 --> 00:38:55.150
I beg you.

00:38:55.150 --> 00:38:57.570
Carry out the justice personally.

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:08.700
Jie,

00:39:09.320 --> 00:39:11.150
it's all my fault

00:39:11.610 --> 00:39:13.650
for not teaching you right.

00:39:14.360 --> 00:39:15.240
From now on,

00:39:15.530 --> 00:39:16.860
I'll provide for you.

00:39:18.070 --> 00:39:18.740
Nobody move!

00:39:18.740 --> 00:39:19.420
Grandpa!

00:39:19.420 --> 00:39:20.530
Zixia!

00:39:21.300 --> 00:39:21.920
Zixia!

00:39:23.150 --> 00:39:25.090
Huang Gongjie, you bastard!

00:39:25.090 --> 00:39:27.070
The Fifth Master kindly pleaded for you.

00:39:27.070 --> 00:39:27.720
Pleaded for me?

00:39:27.720 --> 00:39:29.360
Is that how you plead for someone?

00:39:29.360 --> 00:39:31.320
After pleading, he still cut
off both my arms?

00:39:31.320 --> 00:39:33.720
What are you all standing around for?
Move!

00:39:35.280 --> 00:39:36.970
If I'm going down,

00:39:37.070 --> 00:39:38.470
I'm taking someone with me!

00:39:38.470 --> 00:39:39.340
with me!

00:39:39.340 --> 00:39:40.110
Grandpa!

00:39:40.700 --> 00:39:41.400
Stay back!

00:39:41.400 --> 00:39:42.400
Everyone back!

00:39:42.970 --> 00:39:43.780
Make way!

00:39:44.170 --> 00:39:44.650
Let's move!

00:39:44.650 --> 00:39:45.700
Grandpa!

00:40:05.130 --> 00:40:06.030
Xian,

00:40:07.900 --> 00:40:09.220
what's your plan now?

00:40:10.130 --> 00:40:11.730
Are we really going to Macau?

00:40:12.450 --> 00:40:13.900
Surely the Japanese

00:40:14.440 --> 00:40:16.440
won't actually push into Hong Kong?

00:40:16.740 --> 00:40:19.800
Tens of thousands of Japanese troops
are stationed across the Shenzhen River—

00:40:19.800 --> 00:40:21.380
surely not just for show.

00:40:25.570 --> 00:40:28.300
After all, Hong Kong is
in British possession.

00:40:28.570 --> 00:40:30.950
They've been shouting about attacking

00:40:30.950 --> 00:40:32.450
for over half a year now,

00:40:32.450 --> 00:40:34.180
and nothing's happened so far.

00:40:34.630 --> 00:40:35.780
Honestly,

00:40:36.840 --> 00:40:38.720
compared to Hong Kong,

00:40:38.720 --> 00:40:41.780
Macau is just a small place—
not quite on the same level.

00:40:42.760 --> 00:40:44.290
Haven't I said that before?

00:40:44.670 --> 00:40:45.780
Not moving now.

00:40:46.280 --> 00:40:46.740
With elderly parents

00:40:46.740 --> 00:40:48.340
and young kids in the family,

00:40:48.720 --> 00:40:50.650
we still need to keep a way out open.

00:40:54.780 --> 00:40:55.640
Let's just hope

00:40:55.840 --> 00:40:57.950
Hong Kong stays peaceful

00:40:58.170 --> 00:40:59.370
and nothing happens.

00:41:00.760 --> 00:41:02.020
Let's hope so, anyway.

00:41:04.280 --> 00:41:07.860
[HQ of the Japanese Expeditionary Army
to Southern China, Guangzhou]

00:41:07.860 --> 00:41:09.460
Why are we kept waiting here?

00:41:10.320 --> 00:41:11.780
What's really going on?

00:41:12.030 --> 00:41:13.800
All the generals,
including Commander Sakai Takashi,

00:41:13.800 --> 00:41:14.800
have been shut

00:41:14.800 --> 00:41:16.860
in the operations room all night.

00:41:17.360 --> 00:41:17.450
[Sawa Eisaku, Head of the Japanese
Special Service Organ in Macau]

00:41:17.450 --> 00:41:19.490
Something big—

00:41:21.260 --> 00:41:25.110
something beyond
what we could have anticipated.

00:41:25.530 --> 00:41:29.280
Hana saku!

00:41:30.400 --> 00:41:31.200
Report!

00:41:31.440 --> 00:41:34.700
Imperial General Headquarters,
Telegram 684: Hana saku.

00:41:35.070 --> 00:41:36.530
Hana saku!

00:41:41.050 --> 00:41:42.110
General.

00:41:42.330 --> 00:41:44.420
[Yazaki Kanju, Chief of the Japanese
Special Service Organ for Southern China]

00:41:44.420 --> 00:41:47.470
You two—to my office.

00:41:52.420 --> 00:41:53.470
[December 8, 1941, China Time]

00:41:53.490 --> 00:41:54.260
[In the early hours, the Japanese Navy
launched a surprise attack]

00:41:54.290 --> 00:41:55.210
[on the U.S. Pacific Fleet Base,]

00:41:55.230 --> 00:41:56.040
[creating the Pearl Harbor Attack]

00:41:56.060 --> 00:41:56.780
[and thus igniting the Pacific War.]

00:41:57.470 --> 00:41:58.550
So from now on,

00:41:58.900 --> 00:42:00.760
there will be no force left

00:42:00.760 --> 00:42:01.400
in the Pacific

00:42:01.400 --> 00:42:03.780
capable of threatening
the Empire of Japan.

00:42:03.780 --> 00:42:04.510
Next,

00:42:05.300 --> 00:42:08.010
the Imperial Army's advance
will be unstoppable,

00:42:08.010 --> 00:42:11.230
sweeping across all of Southeast Asia.

00:42:13.170 --> 00:42:14.360
Exactly.

00:42:14.860 --> 00:42:17.660
Simultaneously
with the Pearl Harbor operation,

00:42:17.860 --> 00:42:18.010
the Imperial Army has already begun

00:42:18.010 --> 00:42:18.760
[Yasumitsu Fukae, Lieutenant Colonel,
Consul of Japan in Macau]

00:42:18.760 --> 00:42:20.820
landing operations
on the Malay Peninsula.

00:42:20.820 --> 00:42:23.760
Just now, Commander Sakai Takashi

00:42:23.760 --> 00:42:26.320
issued the action order
codenamed "Eagle."

00:42:27.400 --> 00:42:29.970
All units
of our South China Expeditionary Army

00:42:29.970 --> 00:42:32.360
are now in combat positions.

00:42:32.670 --> 00:42:34.110
At dawn,

00:42:34.780 --> 00:42:38.070
a full-scale assault
on Hong Kong will commence.

00:42:42.220 --> 00:42:45.020
To the victory
of the "Greater East Asia Holy War"—

00:42:45.720 --> 00:42:46.220
cheers!

00:42:56.440 --> 00:42:57.150
So,

00:43:00.700 --> 00:43:01.470
what about Macau?